title: Roads
description: A road centerline dataset that can be used for assigning addresses, geocoding, labeling, and general cartographic display.The features and tabular information in this dataset are continually updated and may change frequently.

title: Townships
description: A polygon dataset of PLSS townships (also known as minor civil divisions in U.S. Census Bureau terminology) in Hubbard County, MN.

title: Tax Parcels
description: The published representation of real property areas, combined with assessing and tax information from CAMA and Tax systems, and organized for consumption in desktop and web applications. This dataset contains redundant geometry in cases where there are multiple units or interests on a given tax parcel.The features and tabular information in this dataset are continually updated and may change frequently.

title: Address Points
description: Dataset containing a point location (generally placed at the driveway entrance) and the official physical address including house number, street name, postal city name, and postal code (ZIP code).The features and tabular information in this dataset are continually updated and may change frequently.

title: Sections
description: A polygon dataset of PLSS sections in Hubbard County, MN
